{"tid":1631550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警告］分化撚全面進場","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:28:34.000Z","uid":326766,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cd958ef1832cc9cdeb28b08a88bb1ef874c0b814","tid":1631550,"uid":326766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"雖然我係P牌第一次開post，但希望大家可以聽我講幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今日港島九龍兩條線大遊行，有好多人都屌班港島撚為左個畫面靚，搞到手足比人圍捕，經過今日之後都知道港島大遊行係行唔通，因為班狗實封死曬，但學班狗咁講 做法唔完美，但可接受要改善。<br />\n<br />\n同埋入夜後不斷有分化撚開post話前線手足失控，亂咁幫人裝修，想引起罵戰想和理非割席，重點佢地係想<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令人覺得前線手足真係冇理智 試圖想造成暴徒既形象</span></span> 求求大家唔好咁易比佢分化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心做錯左咪道歉再嚟過 而家都過去左追究責任嚟做乜，不如試下做好啲文宣好過喇，執著喺邊個錯先有咩用，大家一齊改進唔係更好咩，相信前線手足係有理智 核爆都唔割唔係得個講字，希望大家講野語氣要好啲，記住黑裝修 紅裝飾 藍罷買 黃幫襯 不分化不割席不篤灰，求下大家唔好再鬧交，睇到你地比人引戰鬧交好傷心好心痛<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹係個人推測，政府想將示威者雕塑成暴徒既形象，令同路人都開始分化，大家唔好真係咁傻豬真係比人講一兩句就割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且希望手足們都好好記得天琦話既話，唔好比仇恨支配自己 ，知道我地既手足心入面都好善良好可愛，唔好再鬧交喇好冇，一齊諗下聽日同下一步有咩計劃。<br />\n<br />\n我可能打到1999文筆好差，大家唔好介意，打編野想你地唔好再嘈交，手足齊上齊落，唔好比林鄭班狗得逞，如果睇曬我依個p牌仔打既野真係好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">約定你地喺煲底除罩相見 愛你地</span></span>"},{"pid":"781eb9cb2f15fada6de64a84e811f332b9c5fbb0","tid":1631550,"uid":38170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b567b5d2afc488ffe521479bc6fc705504e96287","tid":1631550,"uid":278212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"［重要］抗議蒙面唔一定要裝修 遊行 可以商場唱歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c54e1b0af386770e51d53fb0de5f0d7bcb6780c8","tid":1631550,"uid":133886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76fe884ba0affccc153bf642682cb46c3f43b2aa","tid":1631550,"uid":42549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不分和勇</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d4cb0a89805b1d8d446f169f7801c2e8aea387ad","tid":1631550,"uid":74244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人分化<br />\n<br />\n和勇合一先會贏"},{"pid":"01361d60033d14a6c474e50ce327c9a5df16453d","tid":1631550,"uid":331133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d83f1cc270b7a279fb57da6c35c711cb83354f","tid":1631550,"uid":290982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n好多可能係popo或者五毛嚟分化！"},{"pid":"1c10f689757857200e89bdbe7b3cd3b5587927ca","tid":1631550,"uid":42549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">分化撚</span>襯香港人上哂街唔得閒上連登<br />\n就<span style=\"color: red;\">鵲巢鳩占</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>死仆街</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e582c46847cc6806c6d5f993c095c7b85dd7ddbb","tid":1631550,"uid":326766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫我推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a